data.name: label12.Text
data.value:
❶ Select Arma 3 and TeamSpeak 3 folders at the top bar of the launcher; ❷ Select your Addons folder at "Launch & Addons Options" tab; ❸ Choose the addons pack at the "More Options" (the one on the top, right next to the minimize button) menu and click the "Rocket"!
Here you can select the options that you wish to use when launching the game. We recommend you to set use -noLogs, -noPause, -enableHT, -skipIntro and -noBenchmark for better performance.
If you want to use some additional addons, just selec what you want from the detected addons box (the one with an eye), then move them to the active addons box (the one with a bolt). To disable an addon just move it back to the detected addons box. Make sure you're using an authorized addon. Don't use addons that can ruin the game experience.
For any further help, give feedback or even report a bug, just follow one of the links in the "about" section.
